{"tid":109700,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人N個生活上嘅煩惱或者問題","createTime":"2017-02-06T06:45:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T07:51:48.000Z","uid":73002,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9d4e68fa4b14da0c35975d5f3f18a9b00b504186","tid":109700,"uid":73002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:45:51.000Z","msg":"其實我係讀產品設計嘅，嚟緊final project唔知應該做啲咩好，想問問大家生活上有啲乜嘢煩惱，而呢啲煩惱又可以比我諗到用乜嘢產品去解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一啲煩惱可以係出門口之前唔記得帶鎖匙之類嘅嘢<br />\n或者唔一定係生活上嘅煩惱，例如可以善用一啲用剩嘅資源，例如水"},{"pid":"d4dc5138ceb7e8135c0bec1362d9d3c0348f1110","tid":109700,"uid":8212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:16:02.000Z","msg":"你應該要留意多啲自己生活上有咩不便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b2ea3a8465d0d0fc036dd994b6370fe5001593","tid":109700,"uid":2193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:17:01.000Z","msg":"考車好驚又肥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c84d529ee736eb0554b6293bf70debba62db22","tid":109700,"uid":56608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:37:48.000Z","msg":"冇女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847720a9343d33932c7f9d3c68d2bf510a09a457","tid":109700,"uid":73002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:39:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吹氣Barbie?"},{"pid":"da58dcf2c47f797ea75a93ef4788a08bcb470ccd","tid":109700,"uid":73002,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:49:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你應該要留意多啲自己生活上有咩不便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實頭先諗到梳<br />\n就係咁嘅，梳頭係我哋每日都會做嘅事。二清理梳呢個步驟你係咪日日做啊同埋呢個步驟會唔會煩到你？<br />\n咁我就諗到一把梳，當你要清理頭髮時，咁一個制就可以將所有嗰啲一支支嘅嘢收起晒，咁你就可以好輕鬆咁樣拉晒啲頭髮出嚟<br />\n又或者你本身個頭好多頭髮，或者啲頭髮係比普通人特別容易打kick,當啲頭髮kick住咗係把梳嗰陣，你又可以咁嗰個掣收起啲一支支嘅嘢，咁把梳就唔會kick住係你個頭度"},{"pid":"5e194efbd6ad4902bdc88104aab55ae1144dfb33","tid":109700,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:51:48.000Z","msg":"煮完嘢食唔想洗碗<br />\n洗碗機又貴<br />\n用紙碗食又好唔環保<br />\n<br />\n可以點解決"}]}